commit.message: Fixed a couple very minor errors that forgot to trim the beginning of text in some cases.
Fixed bug where a lack of display name broke features, now it defaults to name instead.
Mentions work both ways now, epic gamer moment.
Added sending messages direct to any channel via text command.
Fixed some minor bugs, added text-driven commands for listing, monitoring, and demonitoring channels.
Checking if repo is up to date.
Added multiple channel monitoring and multiple person monitoring, plus most recent channel response.
Monitoring of individual channels now works.
Added json compatibility to track which numbers are sent which messages.
Basic reading of slack messages and text messages implemented.
